SECTION 2 — KIT BUILDER MODULE
==================================================

Create a new module:

Kit Builder

Purpose:

Convert protocols into physical preparation kits.

User Inputs:

- Protocol selection
- Duration (weeks)
- Number of patients
- Packaging mode:

  Individual Patient Kits  
  Bulk Pharmacy Kits

System Processing:

Read protocol data:

- peptide names
- dose schedule
- frequency
- escalation
- duration

Calculate:

- total dose required
- total mg required
- number of vials required
- diluent required
- consumables required

Outputs:

Kit Summary:

Peptide Requirements:

Tirzepatide — XX vials  
MOTS-C — XX vials  

Consumables:

Diluent — XX units  
Syringes — XX  
Alcohol wipes — XX  

Final Output:

Total kits required  
Total vial count  
Safety buffer recommendation

==================================================
SECTION 3 — BULK VIAL CALCULATOR
==================================================

Create:

Bulk Vial Calculator

Purpose:

Estimate vial quantities based on dosage requirements.

User Inputs:

- Peptide
- Dose per administration
- Frequency
- Duration (weeks)
- Patients
- Vial strength

System Calculates:

Total mg required

Total vials required

Optional:

Add safety buffer:

Default:

+10%

Output:

Total Vials Required  
Recommended Order Quantity

